div.p:
svasti śrī kovirājakesarivanmakku yāṇṭu 8 Āvatu [[kuṉṟa]][kkūṟṟa][[tu brahmade]]yam ciṟupaḻuvūr [[brahmaṇa]]n cāvānti [[tāmotiran koṟṟaṉeṉ Ivvūr tiruvālan]] {built over}

kkiḻ vāykkā ‡ li vaṭavāy ‡ kkāl nāṉ v[i]ṟṟuk kuṭutta nilattukku kiḻpālkkellai Ivvūr [cā][[vā]][nti] [[nārāyaṇa]]n pāṇṭa[[ṉum]][t tam][[pimārum]] nilattu[kku] [[me]][kku][[m tenpālkkellai Ivvūr]] {built over}

tāṉp peThe vowel –e is engraved before the first –p while it should be before the second –p.rumakka ‡ ḷ nilattu ‡ kku kiḻakkum vaṭapāṟkkellai Ivūr cāvānti tevan subrahmaṇyan ṉi[lattukku te]ṟkkum Iv[[vi]]c[ai]tta perunā[n]kkeThe vowel –e is engraved before the first –k while it should be before the second –k.llaiyuḷakappa[ṭṭa] [[uṇṇilam oḻiviṉṟi taṭi Iraṇṭa]] {built over}

ñcaraikkum viṟṟu ‡ vilaiyā ‡ vaṇam caitu kuṭutten tāmotiran koṟṟaṉen [Ittiruvā]lantuṟai [[caṇḍeśadevakku Itu panmāheśvara rakṣai ||]]
